<!-- =====================================================================
     LAXTLINE — Portfolio Website  (single-page, static)
     ---------------------------------------------------------------------
     Stack    : HTML5 + CSS3 + Vanilla JavaScript (zero frameworks)
     Entry    : index.html  →  css/main.css, css/gallery.css
                              →  js/01-cursor-init.js .. js/04-gallery-video.js
     Sections : Hero · Marquee · Work · About · Services · Software ·
                Contact · Socials · All-Work gallery · Fullscreen viewer
     Media    : "All Projects/" (videos+photos) · "Logo  & Background/"
     NOTE     : Real social handles & email are kept as-is on purpose —
                changing them would break the live account links.
     ===================================================================== -->

